    <header class="page-header">
      <h1>How Darpan Works</h1>
      <p>Follow these simple steps to join or create a meeting in seconds. No downloads or installations required.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="steps-container">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">1</div>
        <div class="timeline-connector"></div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3 class="step-title">Create a Meeting</h3>
          <p class="step-description">
            Visit the Darpan homepage and click on "Join New Meeting" to generate a unique meeting room.
            Alternatively, you can create a meeting link to share with participants without joining immediately.
          </p>
          <div class="step-image">
            <span class="material-icons">add_box</span>
          </div>
          <div class="step-tip">
            <p>Pro Tip: Bookmark your frequently used meeting rooms for quick access.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">2</div>
        <div class="timeline-connector"></div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3 class="step-title">Set Up Your Devices</h3>
          <p class="step-description">
            Before joining, check your camera and microphone settings in the device preview page.
            You can select your preferred audio and video devices, test your microphone, and even
            set up background effects before entering the meeting.
          </p>
          <div class="step-image">
            <span class="material-icons">settings</span>
          </div>
          <div class="step-tip">
            <p>Pro Tip: Use background blur or images for privacy during meetings.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <div class="timeline-connector"></div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3 class="step-title">Invite Participants</h3>
          <p class="step-description">
            Share your meeting link or room code with participants via email, messaging apps, or calendar invites.
            Anyone with the link can join instantly from their browser without creating an account.
          </p>
          <div class="step-image">
            <span class="material-icons">share</span>
          </div>
          <div class="step-tip">
            <p>Pro Tip: Copy the meeting link directly from the address bar during an active meeting.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">4</div>
        <div class="timeline-connector"></div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3 class="step-title">Start Collaborating</h3>
          <p class="step-description">
            Once in the meeting, use the controls at the bottom of the screen to toggle your microphone,
            camera, share your screen, raise your hand, send chat messages, and more. Pin important
            speakers or switch between different layout views as needed.
          </p>
          <div class="step-image">
            <span class="material-icons">groups</span>
          </div>
          <div class="step-tip">
            <p>Pro Tip: Use keyboard shortcuts like 'M' for mute/unmute and 'V' for toggling video.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">5</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3 class="step-title">End Meeting & Follow Up</h3>
          <p class="step-description">
            When the meeting is complete, click "Leave" to exit. If you recorded the session,
            you'll have access to the recording for review or sharing with others who couldn't attend.
          </p>
          <div class="step-image">
            <span class="material-icons">check_circle</span>
          </div>
          <div class="step-tip">
            <p>Pro Tip: Rate your meeting experience to help us improve Darpan.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-section">
      <h2>Ready to get started?</h2>
      <p>Join a meeting or create your own in seconds. No sign up required.</p>
